One page:
- Employer unique identifier with validation [ Type Number ]
    - Autofill name for confirmation
- Employee unique identifier with validation [ Type Number ]
    - Autofill name for confirmation
- Have some questions that are rated 1 to 5 [Drop Down]
    - Rating of do they show up on time?
    - Rating of how they behave under pressure?
    - Work performance rating?
    - Complaints from coworkers?
    - How respected are they at work?
    - How reliable are they?
    - How often do they complete tasks on time?
    - How often do they finish assigned tasks?
- Yes/No Questions [Radio Buttons]
    - Have they shown up intoxicated to work?
    - Do they communicate well?
- How long have they been working for the company? [Drop Down]
    - Less than a year
    - 1 <= to < 5 years
    - >= 5 years
